525
00:27:52,574 --> 00:27:53,774
Mr. Xin.

526
00:27:56,375 --> 00:27:59,455
In a few days, several important guests

527
00:28:00,054 --> 00:28:01,895
will come to my house for a visit.

528
00:28:02,574 --> 00:28:04,094
I also hired a steward.

529
00:28:04,455 --> 00:28:06,975
He manages a few people,
but none of them are suitable.

530
00:28:08,294 --> 00:28:11,534
So I want to ask for a favor.

531
00:28:12,615 --> 00:28:15,494
Mrs. Chun, you flatter me.

532
00:28:15,814 --> 00:28:17,814
It'll be okay even if
you could help me for half a day.

533
00:28:19,734 --> 00:28:22,294
I'll owe the money for now,
but I promise to pay it back.

534
00:28:22,774 --> 00:28:26,094
As you can see,
I really can't leave here now.

535
00:28:26,135 --> 00:28:29,975
Do you have anyone trustworthy
who could lend me a hand for half a day?

536
00:28:30,094 --> 00:28:33,415
After all, we've been
master and servant for a while, huh?

537
00:28:33,534 --> 00:28:35,895
They all can't get away either.

538
00:28:38,574 --> 00:28:39,734
Well.

539
00:28:39,734 --> 00:28:42,935
How about this?
You said you have a steward, right?

540
00:28:43,254 --> 00:28:45,855
Send him to me and I'll teach him.

541
00:28:55,254 --> 00:28:56,895
Mrs. Chun, where is it?

542
00:28:57,375 --> 00:28:59,975
I managed to get this opportunity

543
00:29:00,054 --> 00:29:01,415
through great hardships.

544
00:29:01,494 --> 00:29:03,054
Work hard and keep it up.

545
00:29:04,494 --> 00:29:06,494
Mr. Xin, I've brought him here.

546
00:29:06,695 --> 00:29:08,094
Mr. Xin, why are you here?

547
00:29:08,494 --> 00:29:11,814
So, it's Mr. Lu. Long time no see.

548
00:29:15,494 --> 00:29:18,935
Mrs. Chun. Mrs. Chun, help! Mrs. Chun.

549
00:29:19,494 --> 00:29:22,094
Lu Buping, I'm sorry
to have put you in this situation.

550
00:29:22,094 --> 00:29:23,534
Mrs. Chun.

551
00:29:27,294 --> 00:29:29,494
What are you trying to do?
Stay away from me.

552
00:29:29,615 --> 00:29:31,054
I know martial arts.

553
00:29:31,094 --> 00:29:35,215
Tell you what? My father is the leader
of the martial arts alliance.

554
00:29:35,254 --> 00:29:37,175
If you come any closer,
my weapon may hurt you.

555
00:29:37,215 --> 00:29:38,375
I-I'm telling you.

556
00:29:41,895 --> 00:29:43,294
You know Yin Yang Finger?

557
00:29:43,814 --> 00:29:46,734
When your force is useless,
respect is the way.

558
00:29:47,494 --> 00:29:50,855
When your status is useless,
ability is the way.

559
00:29:51,334 --> 00:29:55,415
When your life is useless,
ideals are the way.

560
00:29:55,774 --> 00:29:58,574
Son of the leader of the alliance.
Do you deserve it?

561
00:29:58,855 --> 00:30:00,855
If you want to be a useless person,

562
00:30:00,895 --> 00:30:02,574
of course, I can help you achieve that.

563
00:30:02,615 --> 00:30:05,294
But you have to accept
that everyone will abandon you.

564
00:30:05,294 --> 00:30:06,734
Abandon me?

565
00:30:06,734 --> 00:30:08,415
You don't have the goal
of being a human,

566
00:30:08,455 --> 00:30:10,054
nor do you have the value
of being a human.

567
00:30:10,135 --> 00:30:11,014
You're a burden to others,

568
00:30:11,054 --> 00:30:11,895
