569
00:30:11,935 --> 00:30:13,294
and even a parasite on others.

570
00:30:13,375 --> 00:30:14,975
You can't stand hardship
nor hear harsh words.

571
00:30:15,014 --> 00:30:18,375
Everyone would abandon
such a haughty person.

572
00:30:19,415 --> 00:30:21,695
I have a goal of my own.
I want to be a hero.

573
00:30:21,695 --> 00:30:24,494
The highest realm of martial arts
is not kung fu,

574
00:30:24,774 --> 00:30:27,254
but to facing everything
every day without shaking

575
00:30:27,334 --> 00:30:29,415
