every day without wavering.

576
00:30:30,455 --> 00:30:33,814
But it is just
a basic skill for a steward.

577
00:30:35,294 --> 00:30:40,935
So how can a hero
compare with a steward?

578
00:30:52,294 --> 00:30:53,376
Tengyun.

579
00:30:57,888 --> 00:31:01,494
Well, am I hallucinating?

580
00:31:01,494 --> 00:31:02,774
What's wrong?

581
00:31:02,774 --> 00:31:04,455
You're clearly roasting a bun,

582
00:31:04,655 --> 00:31:09,774
but why did I smell
the scent of meat bun?

583
00:31:12,774 --> 00:31:15,774
Really? That might just be an illusion.

584
00:31:15,935 --> 00:31:17,135
After all, you are Young Lord.

585
00:31:17,534 --> 00:31:19,455
It's normal you will easily get hungry.
It's almost done.

586
00:31:20,855 --> 00:31:23,774
Tengyun, I really admire you a bit now.

587
00:31:24,294 --> 00:31:27,014
You can bear
the bruises, hunger and scoldings.

588
00:31:27,135 --> 00:31:28,695
You were able to escape from that cell.

589
00:31:30,054 --> 00:31:33,534
These days, I've thought about it
and I really haven't been trying hard.

590
00:31:34,175 --> 00:31:35,855
No wonder my father
always calls me a loser.

591
00:31:37,334 --> 00:31:39,695
Young Lord, don't overthink.

592
00:31:40,494 --> 00:31:43,455
I've grown up in such an environment
since I was little.

593
00:31:44,494 --> 00:31:47,175
Here. It's done. Have the bun first.

594
00:31:48,254 --> 00:31:50,855
Tomorrow, I'll find a way
to get you a meat bun as well.

595
00:31:52,814 --> 00:31:53,734
As well?

596
00:31:55,494 --> 00:31:58,534
I mean, no matter what, I'll find a way

597
00:31:58,534 --> 00:31:59,695
to get you a meat bun.

598
00:31:59,695 --> 00:32:01,054
Since you've been wanting a meat bun.

599
00:32:01,655 --> 00:32:03,455
No, thanks. Tengyun.

600
00:32:04,855 --> 00:32:07,774
I eat the meat bun
while leaving you to gnaw on a bun.

601
00:32:08,615 --> 00:32:10,254
I am not such an ungrateful person.

602
00:32:11,615 --> 00:32:12,975
It's not that bad.

603
00:32:13,655 --> 00:32:19,054
Tengyun, I've made up my mind.
Send me back.

604
00:32:20,054 --> 00:32:21,334
This isn't working.

605
00:32:21,814 --> 00:32:24,094
Just assume you've caught me.

606
00:32:24,774 --> 00:32:26,574
This way, my father won't blame you.

607
00:32:27,935 --> 00:32:31,534
And I should go back
and face everything too.

608
00:32:32,494 --> 00:32:35,494
No. If you go back now, wouldn't that
be like sending you to your death?

609
00:32:35,574 --> 00:32:37,054
Although you can't eat enough here,

610
00:32:37,334 --> 00:32:38,494
at least you won't die.

611
00:32:40,175 --> 00:32:41,375
I belong to the Lord's Mansion.

612
00:32:43,734 --> 00:32:45,294
My mother gave birth to me

613
00:32:46,855 --> 00:32:48,455
not just to have me to be alive.

614
00:32:57,814 --> 00:33:00,014
- What's your name?
- Lu Buping.

615
00:33:00,094 --> 00:33:01,774
You want more water?

616
00:33:01,814 --> 00:33:03,695
I am Steward Lu.

617
00:33:03,734 --> 00:33:05,895
Louder. I can't hear it.

618
00:33:05,935 --> 00:33:07,232
Steward Lu.

619
00:33:07,935 --> 00:33:12,455
Is that all you get?
Do you want to be trash forever?

620
00:33:14,175 --> 00:33:16,215
Steady with one level hand.

621
00:33:16,215 --> 00:33:18,655
Stand straight like a pine tree.

622
00:33:18,734 --> 00:33:20,975
Control the knife with your energy.
It sharpens without a blade.

623
00:33:30,415 --> 00:33:32,494
M-Madam, this way, please.

624
