644
00:34:33,494 --> 00:34:36,455
I am not the magistrate.

645
00:34:36,455 --> 00:34:37,975
It's all because you're generous.

646
00:34:38,014 --> 00:34:39,614
As soon as you show up, it's 30 taels.

647
00:34:39,815 --> 00:34:41,815
